{"tid":1305940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【統戰藍絲】遇上九龍灣肥佬呢d人，記得同佢地講……","createTime":"2019-07-11T03:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T03:43:19.000Z","uid":266060,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0a43e44e6298c844416c99a7da07d380ab31143a","tid":1305940,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:40:56.000Z","msg":"就好似呢句：<span style=\"color: red;\">「你洗過碗未呀，煮過飯未呀，養過家未呀?」</span><br />\n九龍灣肥佬真係好典型的例子<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反映出藍絲嗰種但求搵兩餐嘅心態</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n要統戰呢班人<br />\n最好就係針對返佢地最關心嘅嘢<br />\n話大家都想改善香港人生活<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">例如</span>提高打工仔最低工資<br />\n要有全民退保、長者綜援<br />\n仲有好多人4000蚊都未收到&hellip;&hellip;(下刪1000字)<br />\n<br />\n將香港有幾咁難生活嘅真相，點返出嚟<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每說服到多一個藍絲<br />\n我地就多一分力量！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"88d8b3edfa5d9d5fe95be46095455c3db61b225d","tid":1305940,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:41:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKMofAK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKMofAK.gif&h=caf841ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6557099c7f5a60e6c37638fbad1cafd5b003cb6b","tid":1305940,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faaf3b2b8f2cd1198e610af1ebf9175a46992380","tid":1305940,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}